# Building Unios Hermanos Proletarios

The Falange's strength is gaining, as shown by their activities and their violent presence in the streets. Their fascism threatens to plunge Spain once again into the abyss.

Many in our party are calling for urgent action. The "neorevisionist" faction, led by young socialists, have formed specifically around this cause. But many in all factions of the party are calling for action.

- @not_a_big_deal: The Falange's moment will pass. Let's not get too hasty.
- @economic_crisis
- @major_crisis: We must do something to confront the Falange.
- @iron_front


@not_a_big_deal
on-arrival: nazi_urgency -= 1; left_dissent += 5; neorevisionist_dissent += 15
