The Falange is one of the foremost threats to the Spanish Republic. However, we are still formulating a strategy to confront them, and still trying to build up consensus within our party for action. Check back on this later.

@iron_front
title: Form Unios Hermanos Proletarios!
subtitle: The organization consists of the PSOE, trade unions, and workers' militias.
