The Falange and right-wing threat can no longer be ignored. We must build a new organization to confront them - Unios Hermanos Proletarios consisting of the PSOE, the UGT trade union federation, and workers' militias. We have a new symbol for this struggle.

What does this alliance stand for?

- @unity: Unity, Strength, and Determination.
- @anti: Opposition to Fascism, Monarchism, and Reaction.
- @orgs: The PSOE, UGT, and Workers.
- @republic: Defense of the Republic.
- @all: All of the above.

